briefdescription.para: Initialization function for the floating-point real FFT.

simplesect.para:
execution status
RISCV_MATH_SUCCESS : Operation successful
RISCV_MATH_ARGUMENT_ERROR : fftLen is not a supported length

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: The parameter fftLen specifies the length of RFFT/CIFFT process. Supported FFT Lengths are 32, 64, 128, 256, 512, 1024, 2048, 4096.
This Function also initializes Twiddle factor table pointer and Bit reversal table pointer.
